@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@email = admin@admin.com
@password = admin123
@token = cole_o_token_aqui
@listId = 1
@channelId = 1

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Usuario atual
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar lista por URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/iptv-lists/url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lista remota",
  "description": "Lista propria ou autorizada",
  "sourceUrl": "https://example.com/list.m3u8"
}

### Upload de lista
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/iptv-lists/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

### Listar listas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/iptv-lists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Importar lista
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/iptv-lists/{{listId}}/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar lista remota
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/iptv-lists/{{listId}}/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar canais
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/channels?size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar canais
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/channels/search?term=news
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Grupos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/channels/groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Favoritar
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/channels/{{channelId}}/favorite
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
